Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.48,0:00:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akatsuki has snuck into the country. The village of Konoha seeks to stop Hidan and Kakuzu from proceeding further.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.99,0:00:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the information they received from the Fire Temple, \NTeam Asuma heads for the five black market exchange points.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.50,0:00:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, Naruto is struggling to create a new technique,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.28,0:00:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,undertaking an unprecedented challenge that not even the Fourth Hokage could complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.09,0:00:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.12,0:00:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rasengan's my ultimate technique, but you can do it so easily?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.32,0:00:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had to endure crazy difficult training with Ero-sennin, you have no idea what I went through-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.14,0:00:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, this is just the starting point of what I wanted to tell-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.87,0:00:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you can do it with one hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.59,0:01:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always have to do it with clones...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.69,0:01:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.34,0:01:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H282828&\4c&H282828&}Maybe I should give it another try...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.88,0:01:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll wait for him to calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.59,0:01:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't show you Rasengan just to brag about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.11,0:01:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.88,0:01:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you before that Rasengan is a technique that only uses shape manipulation, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.58,0:01:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shape manipulation?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.00,0:01:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I showed a technique that uses both shape and nature manipulation...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.61,0:01:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By which I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.27,0:01:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Chidori.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.41,0:01:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just showing off again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.59,0:02:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This technique not only uses nature manipulation to turn my chakra into lightning,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.66,0:02:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but also shape manipulation to transform it into an electrical surge, thereby determining its range and power.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.05,0:02:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pay attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.34,0:02:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By using both shape and nature manipulation, a shinobi's attack power increases tenfold.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.83,0:02:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although shinobi who can use both together are pretty rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.75,0:02:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it, more bragging.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.41,0:02:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're now able to use wind nature manipulation thanks to the previous bout of training.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.40,0:02:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you've already reached the ultimate level of shape manipulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.75,0:02:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-! Rasengan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.06,0:02:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.70,0:02:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, that means I can use them both, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.39,0:02:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.92,0:02:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.63,0:02:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have my new technique in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.33,0:02:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Yes, yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.83,0:03:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet this'll be the easiest part!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it was, I wouldn't have bothered creating Chidori.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.97,0:03:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was never able to combine Rasengan with lightning-natured chakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.13,0:03:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need incredible skill to combine nature and shape manipulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.53,0:03:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though perhaps "innate ability" or "sense" would be more accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.08,0:03:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not the only one who had to stop here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.45,0:03:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even my teacher, who created this technique, couldn't get any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Even the Fourth Hokage couldn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.52,0:03:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Fourth took shape manipulation to the highest possible level.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:04:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The result was Rasengan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.75,0:04:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An A-Rank technique achieved purely through shape manipulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up to that level, even I managed to copy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.66,0:04:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's also where things get difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.13,0:04:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Fourth originally developed Rasengan intending to combine it with his elemental chakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, you mean Rasengan's an incomplete technique?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.13,0:04:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good way to put it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.86,0:04:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no telling what the next step will produce. It would be S-Rank level, probably higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.17,0:04:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It may even be impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.43,0:04:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This part can't be taught. It's something you have to figure out yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do... Do you know why I'm telling you all this, Naruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.57,0:05:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're the only shinobi in the world who can surpass the Fourth. That's what I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.39,0:05:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's kill the small talk and continue training after we eat, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, Kakashi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.13,0:05:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a smooth talker.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.41,0:05:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.77,0:05:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tajuu Kage Bunshin no Jutsu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsunade-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.23,0:07:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a message from Team Asuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.87,0:08:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An exchange point?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.95,0:08:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It says those two Akatsuki members are heading towards one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.64,0:08:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The closest exchange point to us...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.85,0:08:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're right by it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.09,0:08:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're about to face Akatsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.04,0:08:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine, Ino. If we do what Asuma-sensei taught us, there's nothing to be afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.32,0:08:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.65,0:08:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's what Shikamaru said to me on our last mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.76,0:08:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chouji...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.46,0:09:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shikamaru's working hard. We've gotta give it our all, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.10,0:09:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Asuma-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kinda relationship did you have with Chiriku?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.14,0:09:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.19,0:09:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're a chain-smoker and you haven't had a puff in two whole days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.58,0:09:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You only stop smoking when something's bothering you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.61,0:09:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.80,0:09:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must be getting soft if you can read me so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.54,0:09:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting? I can read you like a book when we play shougi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.93,0:09:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen you like this since the Third passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.51,0:10:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know that Chiriku and I were both in the 12 Ninja Guardians, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.14,0:10:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say we were like you and Chouji.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.26,0:10:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I hope you never quit smoking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.99,0:10:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never quit, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.15,0:10:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I probably never will, at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.01,0:10:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shikamaru, I appreciate your concern,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.27,0:10:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I didn't stop smoking because of Chiriku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.12,0:10:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now forget me, remember that these Akatsuki guys killed Chiriku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.87,0:10:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means they must have incredible abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.61,0:10:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay focused!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.13,0:11:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make Rasengan in groups of two.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.40,0:11:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And at the same time, apply wind nature manipulation to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.93,0:11:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to tell you what to do here. \NNaruto, it's up to you to come up with the method.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.57,0:11:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.16,0:11:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Add wind chakra...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.56,0:11:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Change it to wind nature!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.46,0:11:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how do I do it when I'm concentrating on Rasengan's shape manipulation?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I wanna know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.96,0:11:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.64,0:12:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too much. He just cut the waterfall...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.92,0:12:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At times like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.15,0:12:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I could just keep quiet,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.14,0:12:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm going to be frank with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.03,0:12:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those soldier pills are disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.41,0:12:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.62,0:12:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I prepared them so they'd be easily consumed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.54,0:12:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch. I'll have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.89,0:12:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.61,0:13:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using the Mass Shadow Clones technique like that must be exhausting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.02,0:13:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.94,0:13:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.09,0:13:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.57,0:13:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now add wind chakra!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.71,0:13:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.13,0:13:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.74,0:13:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to concentrate hard enough when using Rasengan as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now I have to apply nature manipulation on top of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.35,0:13:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like trying to look left and right at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.53,0:13:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it all...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.66,0:13:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to complain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.61,0:14:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tajuu Kage Bunshin no Jutsu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where the hell are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.92,0:14:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.98,0:14:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh... Fine, wait up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.33,0:14:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the exchange point.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.00,0:14:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the fuck did they pick a {\i1}bathroom{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.69,0:14:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.23,0:15:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.14,0:15:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make it quick, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.43,0:15:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mistaking it. That's Chiriku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.91,0:15:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You caught yourself a big one, Kakuzu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.94,0:16:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place reeks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.74,0:16:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go already, Kakuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.98,0:16:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on. I need to count the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.17,0:16:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell whether the stench is the piss or that body, but seriously, it's fuckin' gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.46,0:16:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.48,0:16:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost to the exchange point!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.05,0:16:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay on guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.52,0:17:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.27,0:17:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I look forward to your next capture, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.18,0:17:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hold your breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.71,0:17:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're heading to Konoha to search for a Jinchuuriki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.57,0:17:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I offer some advice, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.22,0:17:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should ditch your partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.00,0:17:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man seems far beyond the influence of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.87,0:17:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.16,0:17:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's definitely uninterested in money.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.32,0:17:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, there's a good reason why he's the only person...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...who can be my partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.13,0:17:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that would be?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.12,0:17:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every one of my previous partners is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.61,0:18:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The second I have a problem with someone, I lose it and kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.84,0:18:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I just can't kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.75,0:18:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.57,0:18:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Concentrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.55,0:18:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mix the two chakras together!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.86,0:18:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, Tenzou!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.36,0:18:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.83,0:19:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.24,0:19:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we keep this up, Naruto's gonna get hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.72,0:19:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that, I don't know if I can keep stopping him-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.30,0:19:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is the only way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.90,0:19:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether or not Naruto completes this technique depends on you, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.09,0:19:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.06,0:20:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond this...is Akatsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.85,0:20:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.98,0:20:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aww, nasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.79,0:20:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I spent all of five minutes in that shithole \Nand my clothes get soaked in the stink.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.28,0:20:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Took you long enough, Kakuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.12,0:20:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's question, brought to you by special guests, is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.56,0:20:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's underneath that bandage, Kotetsu-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.27,0:20:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.17,0:20:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.69,0:20:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you didn't wear it when you were a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.66,0:20:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.10,0:20:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.83,0:21:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh come on! Let us see!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.59,0:21:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to see it that badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.75,0:21:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.52,0:21:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll want to see it more if you keep hiding it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.76,0:21:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does he have zits?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.73,0:21:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe freckles?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.11,0:21:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe even crazy whiskers?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.72,0:21:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ew, that'd be awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.56,0:21:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you out of your minds?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.32,0:21:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though if you all want to see that badly, I'll have to indulge.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.40,0:21:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.06,0:21:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a good look!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.48,0:21:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.81,0:21:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter. In the end, it's troublesome...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.92,0:21:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just about to take it off, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.55,0:22:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They haven't come here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.41,0:22:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.40,0:22:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll stake this place out until they make a move.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.74,0:23:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I dunno!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.50,0:23:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And even if I did, I wouldn't tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.11,0:23:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.34,0:23:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I work him over?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.72,0:23:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll let Ibiki handle him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.22,0:23:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no sign of Akatsuki having been here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.53,0:23:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same for me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.97,0:24:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no indication anyone's come or gone for a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.03,0:24:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's clear that they haven't come by this area yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.72,0:24:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do, Aoba?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.23,0:24:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still haven't received any requests for back-up from the other four search teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.83,0:24:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So no one's found Akatsuki yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.43,0:24:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't be sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.87,0:24:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They may already be in the midst of a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.78,0:24:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.63,0:24:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The best situation would be for Asuma-san's team to make initial contact with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.59,0:24:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two know better than anyone how strong he is, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.72,0:24:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.20,0:24:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and Shikamaru's with him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.60,0:24:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right then. Let's leave this village and set up a new strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.10,0:24:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move out.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.35,0:25:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's analyze all of the information we've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.73,0:25:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At one point Akatsuki was headed towards one of the five exchange points.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.94,0:25:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't received any requests for back-up from the other four teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.72,0:25:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the boss of this bounty collection agency still hasn't come by.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.11,0:25:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.19,0:25:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still a chance that they're heading towards this bounty collection agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.85,0:25:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.73,0:25:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll wait for Akatsuki to come to us, and ambush and capture them!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.72,0:26:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are all of the attack patterns I can think of that the enemy may take.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.15,0:26:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take up positions around the bounty collector's hideout, as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.52,0:26:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.44,0:26:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akatsuki, where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.46,0:27:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Took you long enough, Kakuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.28,0:28:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.62,0:28:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's one down.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.51,0:28:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That freakin' hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.53,0:28:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.47,0:28:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? We hit his vital organs!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.64,0:28:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop shaking, damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.22,0:28:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts like a bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.10,0:28:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he immortal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.32,0:28:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No shit, Sherlock.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.45,0:28:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, who the hell are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.39,0:28:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sash!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.79,0:29:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It belongs to those Ninja Guardians!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.35,0:29:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, god damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.42,0:29:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna have to go back inside that shithole of an exchange point again...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.32,0:29:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiriku!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.29,0:29:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're shinobi from Konoha.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.48,0:29:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been ordered to either capture or exterminate Akatsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.26,0:29:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you Akatsuki work in two-man teams,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.36,0:29:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'd planned on capturing one of you after eliminating the other. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.26,0:29:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you've got some serious powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.34,0:29:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is an Akatsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.09,0:29:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an insane ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.35,0:29:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, my Shadow Sewing won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.33,0:29:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you guys fucked up on the order.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.53,0:29:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's your partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.85,0:29:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He released the technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.75,0:30:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotetsu, Izumo, fall back!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.19,0:30:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that one in the center really is...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.68,0:30:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see the lure of money's got you for once, Hidan.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.63,0:30:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakuzu, stay out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.89,0:30:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to use them for my ceremony!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.14,0:30:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The money's all yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.90,0:30:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakuzu and Hidan, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.74,0:30:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Works for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.70,0:30:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just don't underestimate them. You'll get yourself killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.19,0:30:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like they could pull it off, Kakuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.23,0:30:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they could kill me, I'd let 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.09,0:30:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not happening, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.84,0:30:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he going to do with that diagram?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.65,0:30:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take the lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.48,0:30:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as you see an opening, immobilize the immortal guy with the Shadow Sewing, Shikamaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.38,0:30:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can just give me a couple seconds, I'll cut his head off and hopefully keep him from interfering.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.53,0:30:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too risky!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.11,0:31:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.64,0:31:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.42,0:31:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you get it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.74,0:31:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the best strategy we've got right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.28,0:31:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen Asuma get like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.07,0:31:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're a hell of a lot stronger than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.95,0:31:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumo, Kotetsu, keep an eye on the other Akatsuki and guard Shikamaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.64,0:31:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we know what they're capable of now, \Nshouldn't we pull back and set up a new strategy?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.63,0:31:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not just gonna let us run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.50,0:31:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we run without putting up a fight, we'll be wiped out,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.18,0:31:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Konoha will be in even graver danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.44,0:31:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like sending in a single unit to break through enemy lines. \NSometimes, that's the only move you have!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.13,0:31:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought you hated those kinds of strategies, like I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.05,0:31:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fad(0,320)}When you're up against a skilled opponent, \Nyou need to make sacrifices to protect the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.44,0:32:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me Asuma's going to sacrifice himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.97,0:32:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of them's stupidly strong and his abilities are still unknown. The other's immortal.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.04,0:32:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This really doesn't look good for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.96,0:32:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that doesn't mean Asuma should sacrifice himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.99,0:32:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shougi?! Too troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.22,0:32:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that you're lazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.52,0:32:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also know that you're good at coming up with ways to avoid as much trouble as you possibly can.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.48,0:32:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shougi allows you to work through various situations by utilizing each of the pieces' individual attributes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.79,0:32:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This game is a must for people like you who're good at coming up with strategies.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.32,0:32:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should get a decent grasp on the rules if you read this book.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.57,0:32:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you'll just need to practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.78,0:32:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be troublesome, but I'll have it down in ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.61,0:32:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.73,0:33:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have to hold back, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.92,0:33:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never expected the Climbing Silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.48,0:33:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This book said something about soldiers in the front breaking through enemy lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.96,0:33:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you that mad about losing?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.95,0:33:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. So you used a strategy that calls for sacrifices, like soldiers breaking through enemy lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.68,0:33:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like the rational type of strategy you might use, but I don't like using it very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.52,0:33:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.12,0:33:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess. The Climbing Silver inflicts great damage to the enemy in exchange for sacrificing your own pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.51,0:33:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it's natural for you to lose pieces during the game, but to consider throwing your own pieces away an easy decision...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.33,0:33:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't detach myself enough, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.41,0:33:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not as logic-minded as you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.55,0:33:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna play again?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.46,0:34:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time I'll take it easy and not use the Climbing Silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.49,0:34:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Break through enemy lines?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.42,0:34:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are these enemies so powerful that he thinks we can't avoid making sacrifices?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.72,0:34:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that we chuunin won't even make them break a sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.05,0:34:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we're at a serious disadvantage if he's got to fight them while trying to protect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.99,0:34:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like Asuma said.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.67,0:34:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They could wipe us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.80,0:34:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the best move?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.60,0:34:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're like the rook and bishop.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.42,0:34:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To capture a rook or bishop, you need bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.41,0:34:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need bait that's big enough to make them think they have to chase it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.59,0:34:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not good enough to be that bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.76,0:34:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only one who's strong enough to do that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.52,0:34:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't cut out to be the Climbing Silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.86,0:34:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't end up a sacrificial piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.44,0:34:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not with you behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.98,0:35:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.43,0:35:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may not be good enough to be the bait or make them break a sweat, but I'll make sure we win!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.84,0:35:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you finish your little strategy meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.44,0:35:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow ow ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.44,0:35:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting cut up like that hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.17,0:35:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God will smite assholes like you who don't understand the pain of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.32,0:36:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got some nice looking knives!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.51,0:36:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.23,0:36:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.34,0:36:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm cooked if he gets me with that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.53,0:36:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll chase you where ever you run!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.63,0:36:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shikamaru, keep it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.18,0:36:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has to fight while dodging your Shadow Sewing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.91,0:36:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have the advantage!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.69,0:37:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.06,0:37:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Shadow Sewing technique is making the fight easier for Asuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.16,0:37:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The basic plan is definitely sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.52,0:37:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it doesn't matter if he's got the advantage in a physical fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.81,0:37:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy's immortal, and we've got a limit on lives and chakra!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.39,0:37:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real fight won't start until we capture him.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.23,0:37:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to sit and think!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.34,0:37:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.51,0:37:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.40,0:37:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That stance...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.39,0:37:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you think of Chiriku's technique?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.47,0:37:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His was even more impressive, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.34,0:37:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.98,0:37:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hidan, don't let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.18,0:38:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just shut the fuck up and watch, Kakuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.89,0:38:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.69,0:38:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These two really work well together.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.51,0:38:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like that guy really doesn't plan on attacking us.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.33,0:38:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that it means we can trust him to stay like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.87,0:38:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You almost got him, Shikamaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.56,0:38:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget that, I need you to back me up with something.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.23,0:38:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are too desperate!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.33,0:38:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You keep using attacks that have the highest probability of landing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.32,0:38:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see right through you!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.16,0:38:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you mess around too much when you fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.41,0:38:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.73,0:38:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't escape this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.75,0:39:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I won't dodge.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.05,0:39:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unstoppable bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.38,0:39:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill off the kiddies first!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.08,0:39:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.94,0:39:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're fighting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.22,0:39:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Asuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.33,0:39:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If combo attacks and pin-point combos can't hit him, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.91,0:39:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Katon, Haisekishou{\i0}!
