Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.51,0:39:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He stopped moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.77,0:41:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hidan and Kakuzu's abilities surpass human capabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.82,0:41:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All plans against them fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.66,0:41:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The horrible ceremony involving Asuma is about to come to an end as his friends stare dumbfounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.59,0:42:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shikamaru's scream echoes through the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.33,0:42:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asuma dies! The Naruto Shippuuden Special of Despair and Imprisonment!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.71,0:42:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a full hour special!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.42,0:42:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Airing on Thursday, October 2nd at 7:59 P.M.!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.30,0:42:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unfair! Unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.43,0:42:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.45,0:42:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gorgeous, with a great sense of style to boot.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.94,0:42:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've had a bit too much to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.97,0:42:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.19,0:42:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asuma-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.57,0:42:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I wouldn't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.97,0:42:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're blushing!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.49,0:42:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.19,0:42:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm so jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.80,0:42:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm stuck with Tsunade-sama all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.15,0:42:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but it's a great job.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.38,0:42:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Butcha know, even when we were traveling around together, these were the only kindsa guys we'd meet!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.61,0:42:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh man, at this rate I'm gonna miss my chance to get married, like Tsunade-sama did!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.70,0:42:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably should stop there...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.91,0:43:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatev! I never mention it ta her!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.56,0:43:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm saying-
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.70,0:43:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizune!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.53,0:43:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hear you finish that sentence!
